53
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,200
[SPEAKER_00] to the will of God.

54
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] He quoted one of his favorite Bible verses, Isaiah 6, verse 8.

55
00:02:13,460 --> 00:02:16,659
[SPEAKER_00] Here I am, Lord.

56
00:02:16,659 --> 00:02:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] Send me.

57
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:25,439
[SPEAKER_00] After Charlie finished, I met him backstage

58
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:28,919
[SPEAKER_00] and I spoke to him and I'll never forget this.

59
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:30,560
[SPEAKER_00] I said, Charlie baby,

60
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] please talk to me next time before you say that statement.

61
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] Because when you say something like that,

62
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] there is so much power in that verse.

63
00:02:44,539 --> 00:02:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] When you say, here I am, Lord, use me.

64
00:02:49,819 --> 00:02:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] God will take you up on that.

65
00:02:55,259 --> 00:02:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] And he did with Charlie.

66
00:03:01,060 --> 00:03:14,120
[SPEAKER_00] Eleven days ago,

67
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:18,379
[SPEAKER_00] God accepted that total surrender from my husband

68
00:03:18,379 --> 00:03:21,560
[SPEAKER_00] and then called him to his side.

69
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:26,080
[SPEAKER_00] More than anything, Charlie wanted to do,

70
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] not his will, but God's will.

71
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,560
[SPEAKER_00] And over these past eleven days,

72
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:34,560
[SPEAKER_00] through all the pain,

73
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:39,240
[SPEAKER_00] never before have I found as much comfort

74
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,699
[SPEAKER_00] as I now do

75
00:03:41,699 --> 00:03:44,280
[SPEAKER_00] in the words of our Lord's Prayer,

76
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,719
[SPEAKER_00] thy will be done.

77
00:03:46,719 --> 00:04:03,580
[SPEAKER_00] God's love was revealed to me on the very day

78
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:05,280
[SPEAKER_00] my husband was murdered.

79
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] On the afternoon of September 10th,

80
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:12,240
[SPEAKER_00] I arrived at a Utah hospital

81
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] to do the unthinkable,

82
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:16,199
[SPEAKER_00] to look directly

83
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:19,319
[SPEAKER_00] at my husband's murdered body.

84
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:24,339
[SPEAKER_00] I saw the wound that ended his life.

85
00:04:24,339 --> 00:04:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] I felt everything you would expect to feel.

86
00:04:30,779 --> 00:04:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] I felt shock.

87
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:32,459
[SPEAKER_00] I felt shock.

88
00:04:32,459 --> 00:04:35,060
[SPEAKER_00] I felt horror.

89
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:39,399
[SPEAKER_00] And a level of heartache

90
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:43,139
[SPEAKER_00] that I didn't even know existed.

91
00:04:43,139 --> 00:04:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] But there was something else too.

92
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:52,040
[SPEAKER_00] even in death,

93
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] I could see the man that I love.

94
00:04:54,420 --> 00:05:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] I saw the one single gray hair

95
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,959
[SPEAKER_00] on the side of his head,

96
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] which I never told him about.

97
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:08,800
[SPEAKER_00] Now he knows.

98
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sorry, baby.

99
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] I'm telling you now,

100
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,399
[SPEAKER_00] but never told him.

101
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:13,680
[SPEAKER_00] Didn't want to.

102
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,379
[SPEAKER_00] I also saw this.

103
00:05:18,379 --> 00:05:22,180
[SPEAKER_00] I also saw on his lips

104
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:24,879
[SPEAKER_00] the faintest smile.

105
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:29,180
[SPEAKER_00] And that told me something important.

106
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:33,459
[SPEAKER_00] It revealed to me

107
00:05:33,459 --> 00:05:35,399
[SPEAKER_00] a great mercy from God

108
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:36,360
[SPEAKER_00] in this tragedy.

109
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] When I saw that,

110
00:05:39,860 --> 00:05:41,040
[SPEAKER_00] it told me

111
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] that Charlie didn't suffer.

112
00:05:43,220 --> 00:05:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] Even the doctor told me.

113
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:49,660
[SPEAKER_00] it was something so instant

114
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:50,360
[SPEAKER_00] that even

115
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,879
[SPEAKER_00] even if Charlie had been shot

116
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:54,360
[SPEAKER_00] in the operating room itself,

117
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:57,459
[SPEAKER_00] nothing could have been done.

118
00:05:57,459 --> 00:06:00,240
[SPEAKER_00] There was no pain.

119
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] There was no fear.

120
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:04,620
[SPEAKER_00] No agony.

121
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] One moment,

122
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Charlie was doing what he loved.

123
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] Arguing and debating on campus.

124
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:13,939
[SPEAKER_00] Fighting for the gospel.

125
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,540
[UNKNOWN] in truth.

126
00:06:16,540 --> 00:06:19,680
[SPEAKER_00] In front of a big crowd.

127
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:22,459
[SPEAKER_00] And then he blinked.

128
00:06:22,459 --> 00:06:24,959
[SPEAKER_00] He blinked.

129
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:28,560
[SPEAKER_00] And saw his Savior in paradise.

130
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:43,899
[SPEAKER_00] And all the heavenly mysteries

131
00:06:43,899 --> 00:06:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] were revealed to him.

132
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:49,220
[SPEAKER_00] God's love

133
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:52,160
[SPEAKER_00] continued to be revealed to me

134
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] in the days that followed.

135
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:57,240
[SPEAKER_00] But most of all,

136
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,800
[SPEAKER_00] God's mercy and God's love

137
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] have been revealed to me

138
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,339
[SPEAKER_00] these past 10 days.

139
00:07:01,339 --> 00:07:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] After Charlie's assassination,

140
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,720
[SPEAKER_00] we didn't see violence.

141
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,439
[SPEAKER_00] We didn't see rioting.

142
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] We didn't see rioting.

143
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:24,060
[SPEAKER_00] We didn't see revolution.

144
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] We didn't see revolution.

145
00:07:25,899 --> 00:07:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] Instead, we saw what my husband

146
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:31,879
[SPEAKER_00] always prayed he would see

147
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] in this country.

148
00:07:32,699 --> 00:07:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] We saw revival.

149
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:49,600
[SPEAKER_00] This past week,

150
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] we saw people open a Bible

151
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,160
[SPEAKER_00] for the first time

152
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] in a decade.

153
00:07:52,699 --> 00:07:56,300
[SPEAKER_00] We saw people pray for the first time

154
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] since they were children.

155
00:07:57,220 --> 00:08:00,819
[SPEAKER_00] We saw people go to a church service

156
00:08:00,819 --> 00:08:01,740
[SPEAKER_00] for the first time

157
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:02,939
[SPEAKER_00] in their entire lives.

158
00:08:02,939 --> 00:08:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] Charlie liked to journal.

159
00:08:16,019 --> 00:08:18,860
[SPEAKER_00] And I say this because

160
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:20,779
[SPEAKER_00] he did it to remember

161
00:08:20,779 --> 00:08:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] important moments and sayings

162
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] that affected him.

163
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:26,100
[SPEAKER_00] And one of the things

164
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] he wrote in his journal

165
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:28,600
[SPEAKER_00] was this.

166
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] Every time you make a decision,

167
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:38,419
[SPEAKER_00] it puts a mark on your soul.

168
00:08:38,419 --> 00:08:44,139
[SPEAKER_00] To those of you out there

169
00:08:44,139 --> 00:08:45,600
[SPEAKER_00] who just made that decision

170
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] and took the first step

171
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,700
[SPEAKER_00] toward a spiritual life,

172
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:54,379
[SPEAKER_00] I say thank you and welcome.

173
00:08:54,379 --> 00:09:06,139
[SPEAKER_00] One day, I hope you look back

174
00:09:06,139 --> 00:09:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] and realize it was the most important

175
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] decision of your life

176
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] because it is.

177
00:09:13,539 --> 00:09:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] All of you,

178
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] all of you who are already believers,

179
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,899
[SPEAKER_00] it is your job

180
00:09:20,899 --> 00:09:22,240
[SPEAKER_00] to shepherd these people.

181
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] Do not take that lightly.

182
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:29,100
[SPEAKER_00] Water the seed of their faith.

183
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:32,879
[SPEAKER_00] Protect it and help it grow.

184
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] Every day as Charlie

185
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,679
[SPEAKER_00] rode into the office,

186
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] he would go through

187
00:09:42,139 --> 00:09:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] his contact list

188
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] and I know there's

189
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] many of you

190
00:09:45,340 --> 00:09:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] who were impacted by this.

191
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] He would go through

192
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] his contact list

193
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] and send Bible verses

194
00:09:50,659 --> 00:09:51,620
[SPEAKER_00] for the day.

195
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] He knew that faith

196
00:09:54,220 --> 00:09:54,919
[SPEAKER_00] was a habit.

197
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] The more you live it,

198
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:58,600
[SPEAKER_00] the more it grows.

199
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] But know this too.

200
00:10:02,019 --> 00:10:05,580
[SPEAKER_00] The seed has only

201
00:10:05,580 --> 00:10:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] just been planted.

202
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,419
[SPEAKER_00] The enemy will tempt you

203
00:10:10,419 --> 00:10:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] the most

204
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,639
[SPEAKER_00] in a time like this one.

205
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] God will always be there

206
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] for you,

207
00:10:16,940 --> 00:10:18,259
[SPEAKER_00] but you must choose

208
00:10:18,259 --> 00:10:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] to mark your soul

209
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] again

210
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:23,299
[SPEAKER_00] and again

211
00:10:23,299 --> 00:10:24,519
[SPEAKER_00] in the direction

212
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,580
[SPEAKER_00] of Christ.

213
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] Pray again.

214
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] Read the Bible again.

215
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:40,679
[SPEAKER_00] Go to church next Sunday

216
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:42,799
[SPEAKER_00] and the Sunday after that

217
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] and break free

218
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] from the temptations

219
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,019
[SPEAKER_00] and shackles

220
00:10:46,019 --> 00:10:46,879
[SPEAKER_00] of this world.

221
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:58,100
[SPEAKER_00] Being a follower

222
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:58,700
[SPEAKER_00] of Christ

223
00:10:58,700 --> 00:10:59,620
[SPEAKER_00] is not easy.

224
00:10:59,620 --> 00:11:02,240
[SPEAKER_00] It's not supposed to be.

225
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] Jesus said,

226
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] if anyone

227
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] would come after me,

228
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] let him deny himself,

229
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:09,919
[SPEAKER_00] take up his cross

